{"id": "ChIJERJ44GbKj4ARc9-1ze0Lnv8", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 2183, "displayName": {"text": "Stan's Donut Shop", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Retro, dinerlike eatery with a basic menu of acclaimed donuts, sandwiches & soda-fountain treats.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJERJ44GbKj4ARc9-1ze0Lnv8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210bVVtVkViRmh6UlY5cGFGTkdYMVJ3VDJkS2NrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I've been here three times. The first time, they were sold out by noon. The second time, I found out they only accept cash. The third time, I got there at 10 a.m. and still had to wait in line for almost an hour.\n\nWas it worth the wait? Yes.\n\nThe glazed donut was amazing and easily the best one I tried. The other donuts were good too, but they weren't anything special. I'd definitely come back for the glazed donut.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I've been here three times. The first time, they were sold out by noon. The second time, I found out they only accept cash. The third time, I got there at 10 a.m. and still had to wait in line for almost an hour.\n\nWas it worth the wait? Yes.\n\nThe glazed donut was amazing and easily the best one I tried. The other donuts were good too, but they weren't anything special. I'd definitely come back for the glazed donut.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rashid Khazeiynasab", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106225410961256946451/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUqW0trJBzzkRlwi9V1p8CIILhhp3CC_beS5aclxw49rLytDBM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-21T23:41:14.194866661Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210bVVtVkViRmh6UlY5cGFGTkdYMVJ3VDJkS2NrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210bVVtVkViRmh6UlY5cGFGTkdYMVJ3VDJkS2NrRRAB!2m1!1s0x808fca66e0781211:0xff9e0bedcdb5df73"}, {"name": "places/ChIJERJ44GbKj4ARc9-1ze0Lnv8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SdGIzWkRTakl4Y3kxV1EzbERhR0YxVEZsbVJIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Known for there original glazed donuts.  Best when it comes out of the fryer.  If you like Krispy Kreme, this is 10 times way better.  There dough recipe is top notch and of course they also make various types of donuts.  We went on a Friday also tried there apple fritters.  They make them on Mondays and Fridays only.  I don't know if my taste buds have changed or Stan's had an off day but there original glazed donuts were super sweet just as there apple fritters.  I could only have a few bites from both before I had a sugar coma.  Stan's probably number five on my doughnut list.  I would rank #1 Bernie Beigne in Montreal, #2 Round Rock Donuts in Texas, #3 I'm Donut in Japan, #4 Doughnut Plant in New York City.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Known for there original glazed donuts.  Best when it comes out of the fryer.  If you like Krispy Kreme, this is 10 times way better.  There dough recipe is top notch and of course they also make various types of donuts.  We went on a Friday also tried there apple fritters.  They make them on Mondays and Fridays only.  I don't know if my taste buds have changed or Stan's had an off day but there original glazed donuts were super sweet just as there apple fritters.  I could only have a few bites from both before I had a sugar coma.  Stan's probably number five on my doughnut list.  I would rank #1 Bernie Beigne in Montreal, #2 Round Rock Donuts in Texas, #3 I'm Donut in Japan, #4 Doughnut Plant in New York City.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Peter Jo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104980030335659651905/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8MWD48KgYZ2ZwQw88wZse-mY7VGkwPLjHv1QCQ1z2rb7fV14M=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-28T06:56:03.225225112Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SdGIzWkRTakl4Y3kxV1EzbERhR0YxVEZsbVJIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SdGIzWkRTakl4Y3kxV1EzbERhR0YxVEZsbVJIYxAB!2m1!1s0x808fca66e0781211:0xff9e0bedcdb5df73"}, {"name": "places/ChIJERJ44GbKj4ARc9-1ze0Lnv8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOWk1sazJaM0Y2UTBnNFVGTjVVV2c1YkVWblRYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Been meaning to come here for years but just never managed to till today.\n\nSo bottom line they are a really good donut shop with out a doubt. Great texture on their donuts with nothing more to really say.\n\nThey are cash only though but they do have an ATM if you don't bring any. Also pricing wise they're pretty in line with similar stores so that's nice.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Been meaning to come here for years but just never managed to till today.\n\nSo bottom line they are a really good donut shop with out a doubt. Great texture on their donuts with nothing more to really say.\n\nThey are cash only though but they do have an ATM if you don't bring any. Also pricing wise they're pretty in line with similar stores so that's nice.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Dan Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105247726133662937685/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIEsZW-pnKqMO-JXntK2cGZ0gWcrf9iN7WAZ-Xb3Hgw7giryA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-16T02:09:58.823735986Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOWk1sazJaM0Y2UTBnNFVGTjVVV2c1YkVWblRYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOWk1sazJaM0Y2UTBnNFVGTjVVV2c1YkVWblRYYxAB!2m1!1s0x808fca66e0781211:0xff9e0bedcdb5df73"}, {"name": "places/ChIJERJ44GbKj4ARc9-1ze0Lnv8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSbGFHcEliR1JuV0hGQlkzVjRTRlZPV1cxVU1tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I can never get enough of this place. I love going there on a Saturday morning to enjoy some coffee and the best donuts in the Bay Area. My personal favorites are the chocolate bar and glazed donuts but you honestly can’t go wrong with any. Picking up is sometimes a challenge because of the long line but it moves fast so not a big deal. They have a few seats to eat there so that’s what I always do.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I can never get enough of this place. I love going there on a Saturday morning to enjoy some coffee and the best donuts in the Bay Area. My personal favorites are the chocolate bar and glazed donuts but you honestly can’t go wrong with any. Picking up is sometimes a challenge because of the long line but it moves fast so not a big deal. They have a few seats to eat there so that’s what I always do.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Elie Saliba", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108121803669524211578/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtUL_5s5aSZz95bKYSMSFW8gQgZ5pRlCCPA5WwpxHVfJ1RxRE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-27T03:48:29.037530396Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSbGFHcEliR1JuV0hGQlkzVjRTRlZPV1cxVU1tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSbGFHcEliR1JuV0hGQlkzVjRTRlZPV1cxVU1tYxAB!2m1!1s0x808fca66e0781211:0xff9e0bedcdb5df73"}, {"name": "places/ChIJERJ44GbKj4ARc9-1ze0Lnv8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSVFlWSXpVMW8xYkhOSGNGUm9aVVZaZFhkM1ZuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place is crowded, cash only and has happy donuts. I got a box for friends’ kids, and they finished donut box in 1 minute 😂 I definitely go back here and enjoy slow moment here with combo donut and coffee later. Love the smell, donuts are superb!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is crowded, cash only and has happy donuts. I got a box for friends’ kids, and they finished donut box in 1 minute 😂 I definitely go back here and enjoy slow moment here with combo donut and coffee later. Love the smell, donuts are superb!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ngân Sâu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100081556186537308264/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzaooZneEh32YlAGzGsilO0_v7mU88MWm4OaHT1P4pFItmkWI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-25T00:19:54.330230315Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSVFlWSXpVMW8xYkhOSGNGUm9aVVZaZFhkM1ZuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSVFlWSXpVMW8xYkhOSGNGUm9aVVZaZFhkM1ZuYxAB!2m1!1s0x808fca66e0781211:0xff9e0bedcdb5df73"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJERJ44GbKj4ARc9-1ze0Lnv8/photos/AWCwydg-PwGRD7ZHq0z8cxa9-f5C62Cc7RFT9VSv3SX3LKvtApjIbBr4DTizlSt5SmIefWiscwohX6zF8ZSPwGqbPcQ507QgSVumjauCUmzCNWr6iJIZnJ7z1B36941sfRR12GLbXNZxIQjpKyr4HARSfRATT9Mr13gsFwQp1BSVbtXMaIN4uUP5VeWU9FVExMNtP36F50KBOjGZ4TGb07z-N-NAPh0Q7cqB-FGllWkudcRKPDf6g0GepNLhuzWVrkYy8xkrDtfzkHj54HMgTgk0KAaTClITP-i7iABiRzIXgL9Dd40o6XUl4QxzChqHF4BOuIU0c4-JwmM8i0_Zw9bYQzwZwC7TzEwT21L3JHSG31bDNoy3XjHUgVan6x2XjHaANZBquA1aX7a-oo_6-J7lSoDC4GTt9wmbbK2Wbbg9_KF_7id3IFaGhrPLTrEWpt4_", "widthPx": 4096, "heightPx": 3072, "authorAttributions": 